PDL::Planet

This is a package for manipulation of images, especially
pictures of Earth and satellites.

Image code taken from Xplanet by Hari Nair:

http://xplanet.sourceforge.net/

PREREQUISITES:

perl 5.6
PDL 2.4.1cvs or more recent

INSTALLATION:
 
Installation should be the normal:
 
perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
 
(as root)
make install
 
Best of luck!
 
